data.description: Step into this remarkable 5-bedroom modern home in Aquarian Acres built by Drippe, complete with upgrades and features that meet all your needs. Enjoy a bright, open living space, a laundry room right off the primary bedroom, and 3 spacious bedrooms on the main floor. The kitchen includes plenty of cabinets and stunning granite countertops, and all kitchen appliances will stay, including the gas range! The primary bedroom is large with a big walk-in closet and its own private bathroom. The backyard has a privacy fence and a covered patio for cool fall evenings. The finished basement offers a large family room, 2 additional bedrooms, a bonus room perfect for a gym or playroom, and ample storage. The extra-wide driveway comes in handy if you have 4 wheeled toys! This home truly has everything you could want! A real must-see! Property lines go back approximately 5-6 more feet past the back fence.
